  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to 400\u00124F (200\u00124C).",
    "Thread king prawns, bonito shave, garlic, and lemon juice onto skewers.",
    "Brush skewers with olive oil and season with paprika, salt, and pepper.",
    "Grill skewers for 4-6 minutes per side, or until pink and cooked through.",
    "Transfer skewers to a plate and garnish with fresh parsley and oregano.",
    "Serve with pita chips and tzatziki sauce on the side, if desired."
